* The main entry point to the application.

This is a workaround for the following error when MainApp is made the entry point of the

*

Error: JavaFX runtime components are missing, and are required to run this application

*

* for the javafx.graphics module to be present as a named module. We don't use JavaFX via the
* module system so it can't find the javafx.graphics module, and so the launch is aborted.

*
